General.Name: Nimbus Group AB
General.Description: Nimbus Group AB (Publ) designs, manufactures, and markets recreational motorboats worldwide. The company provides the boats under the Nimbus, Alukin, Aquador, Bella, Falcon, Flipper, and Paragon Yachts brand names. It offers its products through a network of dealers, retailers, and resellers. The company was founded in 1968 and is based in Gothenburg, Sweden.
